values:
Hello ppl,

Well there has been alot going on in the pas couple of months....I won't get in to it here cause I don't really want ppl to kno...it isn't the whole worlds business..but it has been both good n bad..I have been thru alot....I have come out of it feeling older n wiser....Love You All

Jessica

Hello everyone....
wow...it has been awhile since I have actually just sat here and updated this thing...It has been a weird night/day...I wake up to find something interesting in my mail box this morning..and low and behold there is an invite for someone to join my yahoo 360...I mean I haven't seen this guy in years and it brought back some good memories...and all I can say at this point n time is "Wow"... He was a sweet guy then and I am sure he is still a sweet guy now....Still cute too...but anyway I will blabbing and talk to you all later....

FallenAngl/Jessica

Probably no one will ever read this and that is okay....I have come to terms with many things in my life...I have friends and family that love me and that is all that matters...I am ready for that next step in my life but if it never comes I am okay with that...It means that is was never meant to happen in the first place...But if it happens it happens...Alot of things have happened lately but I will not discuss them here because there are certin ppl out there who will think they are funny and throw my weaknesses back in my face...but that is okay I know that I am the better person in the end so they can take their issuses and stuff them....


FallenAngl
